available_filters.f_accountnumber: Account number of any line in the transaction
available_filters.f_amount: Total amount of the transaction (always a positive number)
available_filters.f_contactname: Any part of any contact name (first, last, and/or company), case insensitive
available_filters.f_lastupdated: Last updated (created or modified). Format: yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ss.SSSZ
available_filters.f_memo: Any part of the memo, case insensitive
available_filters.f_note: Any part of the note, case insensitive
available_filters.f_reconciled: Whether the transaction is reconciled: y, n
